&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spearhead AI initiatives within Notebooks, serving as the technical owner for the design, development, and deployment of ML/AI-driven features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape the long-term technical direction and strategy for AI workflows within Notebooks and related products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Champion the full development cycle: from rapid prototyping and defining success metrics/evaluations to running experiments, iterating, and achieving production-ready scale and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive product direction with a strong user focus, always advocating for the best end-user experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinate with other leaders and product teams interested in leveraging Notebooks in their AI-powered workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop robust agent systems, including tools, retrieval and planning strategies, guardrails, prompt management/evaluations, fallbacks, and human-in-the-loop processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay up to date with industry trends, guiding the adoption of new technologies and evolving best-practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
